title: The Foo Zeiters 3/22: NCAA, Krispy Kreme, Elgin Baylor, NBA, Capitol, Ken Jennings
itunes:title: The Foo Zeiters 3/22: NCAA, Krispy Kreme, Elgin Baylor, NBA, Capitol, Ken Jennings
description:
On this edition of The Foo Zeiters Jack and Miles discuss NCAA news and tourney standings, Krispy Kreme giving out free donuts to vaccinated customers, Lakers star Elgin Baylor dies at 86, NBA injuries: Lebron out indefinitely, Ball out for the season, sedition charges likely in Capitol riot investigation, and Ken Jennings departs as guest 'Jeopardy' host and is replaced with Dr. Oz, to fans' dismay.
